OL,3,COne in six infections now resistant to
OL,4,Cantibiotics, WHO warns
OL,6,FA new report from the World Health
OL,7,FOrganization (WHO) has revealed a
OL,8,Ftroubling rise in antibiotic
OL,9,Fresistance, with one in six bacterial
OL,10,Finfections worldwide now defying
OL,11,Fstandard treatments.
OL,13,FBetween 2018 and 2023, resistance
OL,14,Fincreased in more than 40% of the
OL,15,Finfection-antibiotic combinations
OL,16,Fbeing monitored by the WHO, according
OL,17,Fto the report released on Monday.
