OL,3,COne in six infections now resistant to
OL,4,Cantibiotics, WHO warns
OL,6,F"Antimicrobial resistance is outpacing
OL,7,Fadvances in modern medicine,
OL,8,Fthreatening the health of families
OL,9,Fworldwide," said WHO Director-General
OL,10,FDr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus.
OL,12,F"We must use antibiotics responsibly,
OL,13,Fand make sure everyone has access to
OL,14,Fthe right medicines, quality-assured
OL,15,Fdiagnostics, and vaccines.
