OL,3,COne in six infections now resistant to
OL,4,Cantibiotics, WHO warns
OL,6,FData collected from more than 100
OL,7,Fcountries through WHO's Global
OL,8,FAntimicrobial Resistance and Use
OL,9,FSurveillance System (GLASS) highlights
OL,10,Fstark regional differences.
OL,12,FThe highest resistance rates were
OL,13,Ffound in South-East Asia and the
OL,14,FEastern Mediterranean, where one in
OL,15,Fthree infections were resistant.
OL,17,FIn Africa, the figure stood at one in
OL,18,Ffive.
