OL,3,COne in six infections now resistant to
OL,4,Cantibiotics, WHO warns
OL,6,FThese pathogens are increasingly
OL,7,Fresistant to third-generation
OL,8,Fcephalosporins`first-line treatments
OL,9,Ffor severe infections.
OL,11,FIn some regions, resistance exceeds
OL,12,F70%, forcing doctors to rely on last-
OL,13,Fresort antibiotics that are expensive
OL,14,Fand often unavailable in low-income
OL,15,Fand middle-income countries.
